'''伊斯蘭黃金時代'''（[[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]：العصر الذهبي للإسلام）又稱'''伊斯蘭復興'''<ref>''Humanism in the renaissance of Islam: the cultural revival during the Buyid age''，第1、148頁</ref>，其时间跨度在習慣上是指公元762年—13世紀之間的500年<ref>''Arab science in the golden age (750–1258 C.E.) and today''</ref>，近來的一些學術研究將之延展至15世紀<ref name="Astronomy">{{cite book | language = en | author = George Saliba | title = ''A History of Arabic Astronomy: Planetary Theories During the Golden Age of Islam'' | date = 1995年 | publisher = NYU Press | isbn = 0-8147-8023-7 | pages = 第245、250、256-257頁 }}</ref>。在這段時期，[[伊斯蘭世界|伊斯蘭世界]]的藝術家、工程師、學者、詩人、哲學家、地理學家及商人輩出，在傳統學術的基礎上保留並促進了[[藝術|藝術]]、[[農業|農業]]、[[經濟學|經濟]]、[[工業|工業]]、[[法律|法律]]、[[文學|文學]]、[[航海|航海]]、[[哲學|哲學]]、[[科學|科學]]、[[社會學|社會學]]、[[科技|科技]]各方面的發展，並在基礎之上對這些方面實施改革創新<ref name="Science">''Science in medieval Islam: an illustrated introduction''，第270頁</ref>。作家[[霍華·透納|-{zh-tw:霍華·透納;zh-cn:霍华德·特纳;zh-hk:侯活·特納;}-]]寫道：「穆斯林藝術家、科學家、傑出人物及工人合力創造了一種獨一無二的文化，直接及間接地影響到各個大陸上的社會。」<ref name="Science"/>

== 基礎 ==
=== 背景 ===
[[File:Map_of_expansion_of_Caliphate.svg|thumb]]時代{{legend|#a1584e|由[[穆罕默德|穆罕默德]]領導的擴張（622年－632年）}} {{legend|#ef9070|[[四大哈里發|四大哈里發]]時期的擴張（632年－661年）}} {{legend|#fad07d|[[倭馬亞王朝|倭馬亞王朝]][[哈里發|哈里發]]時期的擴張（661年－750年）}}]]

[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]透過7—8世紀前半叶的征服活動而建立了[[阿拉伯帝國|阿拉伯帝國]]，又稱[[伊斯蘭帝國|伊斯蘭帝國]]，那是歷史上最龐大的帝國之一<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = William W. Cooper、Piyu Yue | title = ''Challenges of the Muslim World: Present, Future and Past'' | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=3qwuhK3BBH8C&pg=PA214#v=onepage&q=&f=false | date = 2008年 | publisher = Emerald Group Publishing | isbn = 0-444-53243-9 | pages = 第214頁 | access-date = 2009-10-27 | archive-date = 2014-04-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140421221028/http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=3qwuhK3BBH8C&pg=PA214#v=onepage&q=&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。隨著[[阿拔斯王朝|阿拔斯王朝]]崛起及于公元762年將首都由[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]遷至东方新建成的[[巴格達|巴格達]]，伊斯蘭黃金時代亦就此開启。后起之秀的巴格达与[[唐长安城|唐长安城]]和[[拜占庭帝国|拜占庭帝国]]的[[君士坦丁堡|君士坦丁堡]]并称[[中世纪前期|中世纪前期]]三大[[全球城市|全球城市]]。

阿拔斯人受到[[古蘭經|古蘭經]]的指令及諸如「學者的墨水比殉教者的血水更為神聖」的[[聖訓|聖訓]]影響，強調了知識的價值，使這個時期的穆斯林世界成為了科學、哲學、醫學及教育的知識中心，阿拔斯人則成為了知識的泉源。他們在巴格達成立了「[[智慧之家|智慧之家]]」，穆斯林及非穆斯林學者在這裡聚會，將世界上的知識翻譯成阿拉伯文，是為[[翻譯運動|翻譯運動]]。許多在後來失傳的古代古典著作都被譯為阿拉伯語，後來再被譯為[[土耳其語|土耳其語]]、[[波斯語|波斯語]]、[[希伯來語|希伯來語]]及[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]。黃金時代的穆斯林世界是一個文化大熔爐，聚集、綜合及提升了古代[[兩河文明|兩河]]、[[古羅馬|羅馬]]、[[中國|中國]]、[[印度|印度]]、[[波斯|波斯]]、[[古埃及|埃及]]、[[北非|北非]]、[[古希臘|希臘]]及[[拜占庭帝國|拜占庭]]文明的知識。埃及的[[法蒂瑪王朝|法蒂瑪王朝]]和[[安達盧斯|安達盧斯]]的[[後倭馬亞王朝|後倭馬亞王朝]]都是當時主要的知識學術中心，[[開羅|開羅]]及[[科爾多瓦_(西班牙)|科爾多瓦]]都是巴格達的競爭對手<ref name="Mosaic">''Islam: A Mosaic, Not a Monolith''，第26-38頁</ref>。

紙是這個時期的主要革新，一种理论认为穆斯林通过[[怛羅斯戰役|怛羅斯戰役]]的戰俘獲得了[[造紙術|造紙術]]，伊斯蘭城市[[撒馬爾罕|撒馬爾罕]]与巴格達隨即建立起造紙廠。但匈牙利学者Harmatta推断，在[[蔡伦|蔡伦]]发明纸张后的一个世纪，[[粟特|粟特]]就已经用纸通信了；到了3世纪，纸张已传入[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]地区。<ref name="王治来"> 王治来（2007），中亚通史古代卷（上），pp.284-97, 310-22， 新疆人民出版社，ISBN 9787228109081。</ref>[[李约瑟|李约瑟]]指出早在650年造纸术就已经传入中亚的[[撒马尔罕|撒马尔罕]]。<ref>Needham, Joseph. ''Science and Civilisation in China: Volume 5, Chemistry and Chemical Technology; Part 1, Paper and Printing'' p.296-298, Cambridge University Press.</ref>到了707年纸张已在[[阿拉伯半岛|阿拉伯半岛]][[麥加|麥加]]被阿拉伯人使用。<ref>Hunter, Dard (2011), ''Papermaking: the history and technique of an ancient craft'' p.469, Dover Publications. ISBN 0486236196.</ref>总之，都比怛罗斯战役早。

古中國人用[[桑樹|桑樹]]皮來造紙，適合[[毛筆|毛筆]]书写。阿拉伯人加以改變，用[[淀粉|淀粉]]造紙來配合习惯用[[鋼筆|鋼筆]]的穆斯林。接近公元900年，巴格達上百間的店鋪都有僱用抄寫員与裝訂工，甚至開始建立[[公共圖書館|公共圖書館]]，包括首家向外開放租借書籍服務的圖書館。造紙術又從阿拉伯西傳至[[非斯|非斯]]、安達盧斯，在13世紀傳至歐洲<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Arnold Pacey | title = ''Technology in world civilization: a thousand-year history'' | date = 1991年 | publisher = MIT Press | isbn = 0-262-66072-5 | pages = 第41-42頁 }}</ref>。

這些學術發展與地勢相關，早在伊斯蘭教出現之前，麥加已作為阿拉伯地區的貿易中心。[[朝覲|朝覲]]的傳統使麥加成為交換意見和貨物的中樞<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Andreas Nikolaou Stratos | title = ''Byzantium in the Seventh Century: 634-641'' | date = 1980年 | publisher = Adolf M. Hakkert | pages = 第20頁 }}</ref>，穆斯林商人掌控非洲與阿拉伯、阿拉伯與亞洲之間的貿易路線，影響力非常巨大。以這種商業經濟為基礎，伊斯蘭文明得以發展擴張，與此相對，中國人和印度人的社會是由掌有農地的貴族所建立的。這些商人將他們的貨物及宗教引入中國、印度（[[印度次大陸|印度次大陸]]現有超過4.5億穆斯林<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Amitav Acharya | title = ''Age of fear: power versus principle in the war on terror'' | date = 2004年 | publisher = Marshall Cavendish Academic | isbn = 981-210-340-6 | pages = 第34頁 }}</ref>）、[[東南亞|東南亞]]（現有超過2.3億穆斯林<ref>{{cite book | language = en | title = ''Seminar, 第 557-562 期'' | date = 2006年 | publisher = R. Thapar | pages = 第84頁 }}</ref>）及[[西非|西非]]的一些王國，並將外地的一些發明帶回來，他們會將財富投入在紡織品和種植場上。

除了商人，[[蘇非主義|蘇非主義]]傳教士在傳播伊斯蘭教上亦扮演著重要的角色，他們將這些信仰帶到世界上多個不同的地區，包括波斯、古美索不達米亞、中亞及北非。[[神秘主義|神秘主義者]]則在[[東非|東非]]、[[安那托利亞|安那托利亞]]（[[土耳其|土耳其]]）、[[南亞|南亞]]、[[東亞|東亞]]及東南亞發揮影響力<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = mb-soft.com | title = Sufism | url = http://mb-soft.com/believe/txo/sufism.htm | accessdate = 2009-10-28 | archive-date = 2018-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181009032941/http://mb-soft.com/believe/txo/sufism.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The Islam Project | title = Overview of Muslim History and the Spread of Islam from the 7th to the 21st century | url = http://www.islamproject.org/education/B04_SpreadofIslam.htm | date =  | accessdate = 2009-10-28 | archive-date = 2017-12-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171205095859/http://www.islamproject.org/education/B04_SpreadofIslam.htm | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

=== 倫理 ===
許多中世紀的伊斯蘭思想家在追求知識、意義及價值時貫徹了[[人文主義|人文主義]]、[[理性主義|理性主義]]及科學論述。與愛情、[[詩歌|詩歌]]、[[歷史|歷史]]及[[哲學|哲學]][[神學|神學]]等相關的伊斯蘭著作顯示中世紀的伊斯蘭思想接納[[個人主義|個人主義]]、[[世俗主義|世俗主義]]、[[懷疑主義|懷疑主義]]及[[自由主義|自由主義]]的人文思想<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Lenn Evan Goodman | title = ''Islamic Humanism'' | date = 2005年 | publisher = Oxford University Press US | isbn = 0-19-518914-0 | pages = 第155頁 }}</ref>。

在伊斯蘭的價值觀下，縱使[[宗教自由|宗教自由]]受到限制，但仍能吸引了穆斯林、[[基督徒|基督徒]]及[[猶太人|猶太人]]知識分子，締造了[[跨文化|跨文化]]的網絡，造就了8-13世紀哲學創新最重要的時期<ref name="Mosaic"/>。另一個使伊斯蘭世界在這段時期興盛的原因是對[[言論自由|言論自由]]的強調，可見於哈里發[[阿布·阿拔斯·阿卜杜拉·馬蒙·本·哈倫|馬倫]]的遠親哈希米在一封寫給反宗教者的信件裡嘗試以情理去說服對方皈依：

{{Cquote|把你的論據提出來，說你喜歡說的話，自由地表達你的意見。現在你可以安全地暢所欲言，仲裁者將只會倚靠真理來秉公地作出判斷，免去情感的主宰，而該仲裁者應是情理，真主依此來使我們要為自己的報酬和刑罰負責。我在此公正地對待你，保證你的安全並準備好接受任何情理的判決，不論是有利或不利於我。「對於宗教，絕無強迫」（古蘭經 2：256），我在此請求你自願地信奉我們的信仰並指出你現在的信念是醜惡的。祝你平安，真主保佑你！<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = George F. Hourani | title = ''Reason and Tradition in Islamic Ethics'' | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=l4ylahwsnJ0C&pg=PA95#v=onepage&q=&f=false | date = 2007年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 0-521-03563-5 | pages = 第95-96頁 }}</ref>}}

最早論及[[環境保護主義|環境保護主義]]和[[環境科學|環境科學]]，特別是[[污染|污染]]的論述是[[肯迪|肯迪]]、[[穆罕默德·伊本·扎卡里亞·拉齊|拉齊]]、{{link-en|伊本·賈扎爾|Ibn Al-Jazzar}}、{{link-en|班努·塔米姆|Banu Tamim}}、{{link-en|馬西希|Al-Masihi}}、[[伊本·西那|伊本·西那]]、{{link-en|阿里·伊本·里德萬|Ali ibn Ridwan}}、{{link-en|阿卜杜·拉蒂夫|Abd-el-latif}}及{{link-en|伊本·納菲斯|Ibn al-Nafis}}所寫的阿拉伯語文章。他們的著作包含了不少關於污染的論題，如[[空氣污染|空氣污染]]、[[水污染|水污染]]、[[土壤污染|土壤污染]]、[[城市固體廢物|城市固體廢物]]及一些地區的[[環境影響評價|環境影響評價]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = L. Gari  | title = ''Arabic Treatises on Environmental Pollution up to the End of the Thirteenth Century'' | journal = Environment and History | volume = 8 | issue = 4 | pages = 475-488 | year = 2002 }}</ref>。[[科爾多瓦_(西班牙)|科爾多瓦]]和[[安達盧斯|安達盧斯]]首先出現垃圾桶及收集垃圾的[[污染物排放控制技術|廢物處理設施]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Frederick B. Artz | title = ''The Mind of the Middle Ages'' | date = 1980年 | publisher = University of Chicago Press | isbn = 978-0-226-02840-8 | pages = 第148-150頁 }}</ref>。

=== 體系 ===
{{see|伊斯蘭學校|沙里亞法規}}

一些在古代前所未有的教學科研體系起源於早期的伊斯蘭世界，最著名的有[[公立醫院|公立醫院]]（取代了[[睡眠神廟|睡眠神廟]]）<ref name="Copernicus">{{cite book | language = en | author = Peter Barrett、Peter Barrett | title = ''Science and theology since Copernicus: the search for understanding'' | date = 2004年 | publisher = Continuum International Publishing Group | isbn = 0-567-08969-X | pages = 第18頁 }}</ref>、[[精神科醫院|精神科醫院]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Ibrahim B. Syed PhD | title = ''Islamic Medicine: 1000 years ahead of its times'' | journal = Journal of the Islamic Medical Association | issue = 2 | pages = 2-9 | year = 2002 }}</ref>、公共圖書館、借閱圖書館、頒授[[學位|學位]]的[[大學|大學]]及作為[[研究所|研究所]]的[[天文台|天文台]]<ref name="Copernicus"/>。

首先頒授[[畢業文憑|畢業文憑]]的大學是中世紀伊斯蘭的[[穆斯林醫院|穆斯林醫院]]，在九世紀起，穆斯林醫院開始向合資格行醫的伊斯蘭醫學生頒授醫學畢業文憑<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = cyberistan.org | title = Quotations on Islamic Civilization | url = http://www.cyberistan.org/islamic/quote2.html | author = John Bagot Glubb | accessdate = 2009-10-29 | archive-date = 2019-05-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190523055629/http://www.cyberistan.org/islamic/quote2.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]][[非斯|非斯]]的[[卡魯因大學|卡魯因大學]]被[[金氏世界紀錄大全|金氏世界紀錄大全]]認可為最古老的學位頒授大學，該校於859年建成<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Guinness Books | title = ''The Guinness Book of World Records 1998'' | date = 1998年 | publisher = Guinness Pub. | isbn = 0-9652383-5-0 | pages = 第242頁 }}</ref>。建於975年埃及開羅的[[艾資哈爾大學|艾資哈爾大學]]頒授多種學位，包括[[研究生院|研究生學位]]，被視為第一所成熟的大學。[[博士|博士]]的起源可追溯至中世紀伊斯蘭學校的[[教統|教統]]，這些學校教授[[沙里亞法規|伊斯蘭法律]]<ref name="Scholasticism">{{cite journal | language = en | author = George Makdisi | title = ''Scholasticism and Humanism in Classical Islam and the Christian West'' | journal = Journal of the American Oriental Society | volume = 109 | issue = 2 | pages = 175-182 | year = 1989 | doi = 10.2307/604423 }}</ref>。

近十世紀，[[科爾多瓦_(西班牙)|科爾多瓦]]已擁有700所清真寺、60,000所宮殿及70所圖書館<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Graham Faiella | title = ''Spain: a primary source cultural guide'' | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=Y0mduwXyBPkC&pg=PT31#v=onepage&q=&f=false | date = 2004年 | publisher = The Rosen Publishing Group | isbn = 0-8239-4002-0 | pages = 第28頁 | access-date = 2009-10-29 | archive-date = 2013-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131020021440/http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=Y0mduwXyBPkC&pg=PT31#v=onepage&q=&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>，當中最大的圖書館藏書量達600,000本<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Antti P. Balk | title = ''Saints & Sinners: An Account of Western Civilization'' | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=gVvcTx3jgXcC&pg=PA275#v=onepage&q=&f=false | date = 2008年 | publisher = Thelema Publications | isbn = 952-570-000-3 | pages = 第275頁 | access-date = 2009-10-29 | archive-date = 2013-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131020021529/http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=gVvcTx3jgXcC&pg=PA275#v=onepage&q=&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在整個[[安達盧斯|安達盧斯]]，每年都會出版60,000篇論文、詩詞、論證及文選<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = John Gill | title = ''Andalucia: A Cultural History'' | url = https://archive.org/details/andaluciacultura0000gill | date = 2008年 | publisher = Oxford University Press US | isbn = 0-19-537610-2 | pages = 第100頁 }}</ref>。開羅的圖書館藏有200萬本圖書<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=Encyclopedia of Alternative Medicine |title=Unani-tibbi |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_g2603/is_0007/ai_2603000716/ |author=Patricia Skinner |date=06-04-2001 |accessdate=2009-10-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120629144443/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_g2603/is_0007/ai_2603000716/ |archivedate=2012-06-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，而[[的黎波里_(黎巴嫩)|的黎波里]]圖書館在被[[十字軍東征|十字軍]]摧毀之前的藏書量據聞多達300萬本<ref>{{cite book | language = en | title = ''Oliver Optic's magazine: Our boys and girls'' | date =  1869年 | publisher = Lee and Shepard | series = 第5-6冊 | pages = 第560頁 }}</ref>。儘管現在只有少部分現存的阿拉伯科學著作被研習，中世紀阿拉伯重要的原創數學著作在數量上遠超於重要性相當的中世紀[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]和[[希臘語|希臘語]]數學著作的總和<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = N. M. Swerdlow | title = ''Montucla's Legacy: The History of the Exact Sciences'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-the-history-of-ideas_1993-04_54_2/page/299 | journal = Journal of the History of Ideas | volume = 54 | issue = 2 | pages = 299-328 | year = 1993 }}</ref>。[[麥吉爾大學|麥吉爾大學]]的[[科學史|科學史家]]賈米勒·拉格普稱「現時只有少於5%可找到的阿拉伯文獻被研究過」<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Jamil Ragip | title = ''When did Islamic science die (and who cares)?'' | journal = Viewpoint (BJHS) | volume = 85 | pages = 1-4 | year = 2008 }}</ref>，一位俄羅斯史學家也指出這些手稿和著作的數量：

{{Cquote|阿拉伯學者文學研究的成果可在那些海量的現存著作（約數十萬）及手稿（不少於500萬）裡反映出來，數量相當驚人，只有印刷時代可以與之比擬。<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = O.B. Frolova  | title = ''Some Notes on the Arabic Manuscripts and Collections in the Library of the Oriental Faculty of the St. Petersburg University'' | journal = Manuscripta Orientalia: International Journal for Oriental Manuscript Research | volume = 2 | pages = 36-44| year = 1996 }}</ref>}}

現代圖書館不少獨特的特色引入到伊斯蘭世界，圖書館不僅是手稿的收集處，也是公共和借閱圖書館、教授和傳播知識思想的中心、舉行會議和討論的地方，有時會是學者的宿處及供學生使用的[[寄宿學校|寄宿學校]]。[[館藏目錄|館藏目錄]]的意念也在中世紀伊斯蘭的圖書館推行，書籍被劃分為具體的類型和範疇<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Etan Kohlberg | title = ''A medieval Muslim scholar at work: Ibn Ṭāwūs and his library'' | date = 1992年 | publisher = BRILL | isbn = 90-04-09549-7 | pages = 第74頁 }}</ref>。

[[諾曼征服|諾曼征服]]後的[[諾曼人|諾曼人]]、[[西西里酋長國|西西里酋長國]]及十字軍東征時期的十字軍將伊斯蘭法律和[[費格赫|律學]]引進到英國，形成了多個基本[[英美法系|英美法系]]體制的元素。具體地說，「英國皇家契約的債務訴訟出自伊斯蘭的阿格德（Aqd）、英國的[[新近侵奪敕令|新近侵奪敕令]]源自伊斯蘭的伊斯提赫卡格（Istihqaq）、英國的[[陪審制|陪審制]]來自伊斯蘭的拉菲夫（Lafif）」<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = JA Makdisi | title = ''The Islamic Origins of the Common Law'' | journal = North Carolina Law Review | volume = 77 | year = 1998 }}</ref>。[[信託法|信託法]]、[[慈善信託|慈善信託]]、[[代理|代理]]、[[物權擔保|物權擔保]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Gamal Moursi Badr | title = ''Islamic Law: Its Relation to Other Legal Systems'' | journal = The American Journal of Comparative Law 26 | volume = 26 | issue = 2 | pages = 187-198 | year = 1978 | doi = 10.2307/839667 }}</ref>、[[訴訟|訴訟]]及[[醫學同行審查|醫學同行審查]]<ref name="peer-review">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Ray Spier | title = ''The history of the peer-review process'' | journal = Trends in Biotechnology | volume = 20 | issue = 8 | pages = 357-358 | year = 2002 }}</ref>等法制俱來自伊斯蘭法律。其他諸如「教學執照」 、「[[英國律師學院|英國律師學院]]」、「歐洲的[[有限合夥|有限合夥]]」都可能源自伊斯蘭法律。一些學者認為伊斯蘭法律奠下了普通法的根基<ref name="Scholasticism"/>。

=== 通才 ===
伊斯蘭黃金時代另一個特點就是穆斯林[[通才|通才]]的湧現，他們被稱為「哈基姆」（Hakeems），對於宗教及世俗的各個知識領域都作出貢獻，相當於歐洲[[文藝復興|文藝復興]]時期的「文藝復興人」<ref name="Tapestry">{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Center for Contemporary Arab Studies, Georgetown University | title = Tapestry of Travel | url = http://ccas.georgetown.edu/files/CCAS_Tapestry_of_Travel_lores.pdf | author = Karima Alavi | accessdate = 2009-10-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090327110751/http://ccas.georgetown.edu/files/CCAS_Tapestry_of_Travel_lores.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-27 }}</ref><ref>''Science in medieval Islam: an illustrated introduction''，第21頁</ref>。在伊斯蘭黃金時代時期，具有多個領域知識的通才學者比專注於某一領域的學者更為普遍<ref name="Tapestry"/>。

[[比魯尼|比魯尼]]、[[賈希茲|賈希茲]]、肯迪、[[伊本·西那|伊本·西那]]、[[穆罕默德·伊德里西|穆罕默德·伊德里西]]、[[伊本·巴哲|伊本·巴哲]]、[[伊本·祖爾|伊本·祖爾]]、[[伊本·圖菲利|伊本·圖菲利]]、[[伊本·魯世德|伊本·魯世德]]、{{link-en|伊瑪目·蘇尤蒂|Imam al-Suyuti}}<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Islamic Philosophy, Routledge Encyclopedia of Philosophy | title = Science in Islamic philosophy | url = http://www.muslimphilosophy.com/ip/rep/H016.htm | author = Ziauddin Sardar | date = 1998年 | accessdate = 2009-10-30 | archive-date = 2018-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180526222143/http://www.muslimphilosophy.com/ip/rep/H016.htm | dead-url = yes }}</ref>、[[賈比爾|賈比爾]]<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = United States National Library of Medicine | title = Bio-Bibliographies | url = http://www.nlm.nih.gov/hmd/arabic/bioJ.html | accessdate = 2009-10-30 | archive-date = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101064752/https://www.nlm.nih.gov/hmd/arabic/bioJ.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>、{{link-en|阿拔斯·伊本·弗納斯|Abbas Ibn Firnas}}<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Lynn Townsend White, Jr. | title = ''Eilmer of Malmesbury, an Eleventh Century Aviator: A Case Study of Technological Innovation, Its Context and Tradition'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_technology-and-culture_spring-1961_2_2/page/97 | journal = Technology and Culture | volume = 2 | issue = 2 | pages = 97-111 | year = 1961 }}</ref>、[[海什木|海什木]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Sami Hamarneh | title = ''Review: Hakim Mohammed Said, Ibn al-Haitham'' | journal = Isis | volume = 63 | issue = 1 | pages = 118-119 | year = 1972 }}</ref>、伊本·納菲斯<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=Encyclopedia of Islamic World |title=Ibnul-Nafees As a Philosopher |url=http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/drroubi.html |author=Dr. Abu Shadi Al-Roubi |accessdate=2009-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080206072116/http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/drroubi.html |archivedate=2008-02-06 }}</ref>、[[伊本·赫勒敦|伊本·赫勒敦]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Marvin E. Gettleman and Stuart Schaar | title = ''The Middle East and Islamic World Reader'' | url = https://archive.org/details/middleeastislami0000unse | date = 2003年 | publisher = Grove Press | isbn = 0-8021-3936-1 | pages = 第54頁 }}</ref>、[[花剌子密|花剌子密]]、[[麥斯歐迪|麥斯歐迪]]、{{link-en|穆卡達西|Al-Muqaddasi}}及[[納西爾丁·圖西|納西爾丁·圖西]]<ref name="Tapestry"/>都是著名的穆斯林通才。

== 經濟 ==
=== 地理大發現 ===
伊斯蘭黃金時代的伊斯蘭帝國顯著地促進了[[全球化|全球化]]，許多原本孤立的地區和文明透過與穆斯林探險家、水手、學者、商人及旅行者的交流而開始把他們的知識、經商、經濟融合。有些人將這個時期稱為「伊斯蘭大同」或「非亞[[地理大發現|地理大發現]]」，西亞及北非的商人和探險家（當中大部分都是穆斯林，另有少數猶太商人）遊歷了[[舊大陸|舊大陸]]的大部分地區，在大部分的亞洲、非洲及部分歐洲地區建立了早期的[[世界經濟|世界經濟]]<ref name="Eastern">{{cite book | language = en | author = John M. Hobson | title = ''The Eastern Origins of Western Civilisation'' | date = 2004年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 0-521-54724-5 | pages = 第29-30頁 }}</ref>，他們的貿易網路西達[[大西洋|大西洋]]和[[地中海|地中海]]，東至[[印度洋|印度洋]]和[[中國海|中國海]]<ref name="Capitalism">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Subhi Y. Labib | title = ''Capitalism in Medieval Islam'' | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-economic-history_1969-03_29_1/page/79| journal = The Journal of Economic History | volume = 29 | issue = 1 | pages = 79-96 | year = 1969 }}</ref>，有助伊斯蘭帝國（包括哈里發、倭馬亞王朝、阿拔斯王朝、法蒂瑪王朝）在7至13世紀成為領先世界的龐大經濟勢力。一些當代的中世紀阿拉伯研究報告指出，安達盧斯及[[馬格里布|馬格里布]]的穆斯林探險家可能在9-14世紀間橫渡過大西洋<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = S. A. H. Ahsani  | title = ''Muslims in Latin America: a survey'' | journal = Journal of Muslim Minority Affairs | volume = 5 | issue = 2 | pages = 454-463 | year = 1984 }}</ref>。

=== 農業革命 ===
伊斯蘭黃金時代發生了根本的農業改革，被稱為「穆斯林農業革命」或「[[阿拉伯農業革命|阿拉伯農業革命]]」<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Thomas F. Glick | title = ''Noria Pots in Spain'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_technology-and-culture_1977-10_18_4/page/644 | journal = Technology and Culture | volume = 18 | issue = 4 | pages = 644-650 | year = 1977 }}</ref>。由於穆斯林商人在[[舊大陸|舊大陸]]建立了世界經濟，許多的種植和農業技術得以在伊斯蘭世界各地傳播，而且改良了來自伊斯蘭世界以外的種植農業技術。原本不在伊斯蘭世界生產的[[農作物|農作物]]，如非洲的[[高粱|高粱]]、中國的[[柑橘屬|柑橘]]、印度的[[杧果屬|杧果]]、[[稻|稻]]，還有[[棉花|棉花]]、[[甘蔗|甘蔗]]都被引進及分佈在伊斯蘭各地<ref name="Diffusion">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Andrew M. Watson | title = ''The Arab Agricultural Revolution and Its Diffusion, 700-1100'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-economic-history_1974-03_34_1/page/8 | journal = The Journal of Economic History | volume = 34 | issue = 1 | pages = 8-35 | year = 1974}}</ref>。有些人將這種大量農作物的散播稱為「農作物全球化」<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = FSTC | title = The Globalisation of Crops | url = http://www.muslimheritage.com/topics/default.cfm?ArticleID=229 | accessdate = 1-11-2009 | archive-date = 2014-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102191037/http://www.muslimheritage.com/topics/default.cfm?ArticleID=229 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，加上[[農業機械化|農業機械化]]加快，導致了伊斯蘭世界的經濟、人口分佈、[[植被|植被]]分佈、農產品、居群水平、城市化、勞動力分佈、相關產業、烹飪、飲食、服裝等各方面都作出了重大的轉變<ref name="Diffusion"/>。

在穆斯林農業革命時期，[[食糖|食糖]]產品被阿拉伯人改良，並轉變成大型產業，阿拉伯人率先建造了製糖廠及糖料種植園。自8世紀始，阿拉伯人及[[柏柏爾人|柏柏爾人]]將食糖傳遍至整個伊斯蘭帝國<ref name="Transmission">{{cite web |language=en |publisher=history-science-technology.com |title=Transfer Of Islamic Technology To The West, Part II: Transmission Of Islamic Engineering |url=http://www.history-science-technology.com/Articles/articles%2071.htm |author=Ahmad Y Hassan |accessdate=1-11-2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080218171021/http://www.history-science-technology.com/Articles/articles%2071.htm |archivedate=2008-02-18 }}</ref>。

穆斯林引進了[[經濟作物|經濟作物]]及現代的[[輪耕|輪耕]]系統<ref name="capitalism">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Jairus Banaji | title = ''Islam, the Mediterranean and the rise of capitalism'' | journal = Historical Materialism | volume = 15 | issue = 1 | pages = 47-74| year = 2007年 }}</ref>，土地每兩年會有四次或以上的收成，冬夏季作物相互交替。如種植一些生長期較短的作物如[[菠菜|菠菜]]、[[茄|茄]]，每年的收成次數可達3次或以上。在[[也門|也門]]部分地區，小麥每年可收割兩次，伊拉克的稻亦然<ref name="Diffusion"/>。穆斯林根據以下這些因素發展出農業科學：精密的輪耕系統、成熟的灌溉技術，引進多種作物，這些作物都經過了研究及記錄，包括它們所適合生長的季節、土地及所需水分。他們制作了不少農業及植物的百科全書，當中包含了一些精確的資料<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Al-Hassani、Woodcock and Saoud | title = ''Muslim heritage in Our World'' | date = 2007年 | publisher = FSTC publishing | pages = 第102-123頁 }}</ref>。

=== 市場經濟 ===
伊斯蘭國家出現了原始的[[資本主義|資本主義]]和[[自由市場|自由市場]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Edward Miller、Michael Moïssey Postan、Cynthia Postan | title = ''The Cambridge Economic History of Europe: Trade and industry in the Middle Ages'' | date = 1987年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 0-521-08709-0 | pages = 第437頁 }}</ref>，在8至12世紀期間，伊斯蘭國家發展出[[市場經濟|市場經濟]]及[[商家資本主義|商家資本主義]]的雛形，一些人稱之為「伊斯蘭資本主義」<ref name="Capitalism" />。穩定且高值的[[通貨|通貨]]流通性的提高及各地貨幣政策的融合形成了朝氣勃勃的[[貨幣經濟|貨幣經濟]]。在這段時期，經濟學者及商人引入了一些創新的企業經營技巧及商業組織，包括早期的[[股份公司|股份公司]]、信用卡、大企業、[[契約|契約]]、[[可轉讓票據|可轉讓票據]]、長途[[國際貿易|國際貿易]]、[[合伙企業|合伙企業]]（如[[有限合伙|有限合伙]]），還有早期的[[金融信用|金融信用]]、[[債務|債務]]、[[會計利潤|會計利潤]]、虧損、[[資本|資本]]、[[資本積累|資本積累]]<ref name="capitalism"/>、[[流動資金|流動資金]]、[[資本支出|資本支出]]、[[收入|收入]]、[[支票|支票]]、[[本票|本票]]、信託、[[創業公司|創業公司]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Timur Kuran | title = ''The Absence of the Corporation in Islamic Law: Origins and Persistence'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-comparative-law_fall-2005_53_4/page/785 | journal = American Journal of Comparative Law | volume = 53 | pages = 785-834 | year = 2005}}</ref>、[[活期存款|活期存款]]、[[往來戶口|往來戶口]]、[[典當|典當]]、[[貸款|貸款]]、[[匯率|匯率]]、[[銀行|銀行]]、貨幣兌換、[[收支總賬|收支總賬]]、[[存款|存款]]、轉讓、[[複式簿記|複式簿記]]<ref name="Capitalism" />及[[訴訟|訴訟]]<ref name="peer-review"/>。獨立於國家、與股份有限公司相類似的組織企業也在中世紀的伊斯蘭世界出現。自13世紀起，這些資本概念被中世紀的歐洲採納並得到進一步的發展<ref name="capitalism"/>。

商人依靠的[[契約|契約]]體系非常有效，商人以富裕投資者或合夥投資者借給他們的金錢進行買賣，收取佣金，這些投資者多是穆斯林、基督徒及猶太人。近來在埃及[[猶太會堂|猶太會堂]]發現的一批文獻揭示出這些中世紀商人的資料。商業合伙成立了許多[[合資公司|合資公司]]，他們的親屬紐帶使他們得以建立起遙距的貿易網絡。這種網絡可使巴格達的銀行承擔錢財，並在西班牙兌現，形成了當今的支票體系。每當商品透過這些網絡通過一些城市的時候，這些城市都會向這些商品徵稅，導致抵達目的地的商品價格高昂。穆斯林及猶太人所作出的這些革新奠下了現代[[經濟體系|經濟體系]]的基礎。

雖然中世紀時的伊斯蘭經濟與原型資本主義近似，一些學者同時也發現中世紀時出現了與此相對的[[伊斯蘭經濟法學|伊斯蘭經濟法學]]及[[共產主義|共產主義]]，包括[[天課|天課]]及[[里巴|里巴]]（伊斯蘭法所禁止的利息）<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Bernard Lewis | title = ''Communism and Islam'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_international-affairs_1954-01_30_1/page/n4 | journal = International Affairs  | volume = 30 | issue = 1 | pages = 1-12 | year = 1954}}</ref>。

=== 工業增長 ===
{{see|伊斯蘭世界的發明}}
[[File:Jabir_ibn_Hayyan.jpg|thumb]]為化學引進了[[科學方法|實驗法]]，開創了[[化學工業|化學]]及[[香水|香水]]產業。]]

伊斯蘭世界的穆斯林工程師創造了一系列創新的[[水力資源|水力]]工業用途及用於工業的[[潮汐能|潮汐能]]、[[風能|風能]]、[[蒸汽機|蒸汽機]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Ahmad Y Hassan | title = ''Taqi al-Din and Arabic Mechanical Engineering'' | date = 1976年 | publisher = Institute for the History of Arabic Science, University of Aleppo | pages = 第34-35頁 }}</ref>、[[石油|石油]]等[[化石燃料|化石燃料]]<ref>''Islam and Science, Medicine, and Technology''，第29頁</ref>，還發展出早期的工業區。伊斯蘭世界用於工業的水力磨坊可追溯至七世紀，橫向及縱向輪水車在九世紀以後已被廣泛使用。各式各樣的磨坊工廠亦已被伊斯蘭世界所採用，包括早期的縮絨廠、制粉加工廠、脫殼機、造紙廠、鋸木廠、船舶廠、碎石廠、煉鋼廠、製糖廠、潮水動力工廠及風車。到11世紀，伊斯蘭各地區已遍佈這些營運當中的工廠，分佈在安達盧斯、北非、中東及中亞<ref name="Industrial">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Adam Robert Lucas | title = ''Industrial Milling in the Ancient and Medieval Worlds: A Survey of the Evidence for an Industrial Revolution in Medieval Europe'' | journal = Technology and Culture | volume = 46 | issue = 1 | pages = 1-30 | year = 2005 }}</ref>。穆斯林工程師又發明了[[曲軸|曲軸]]、[[水輪機|水輪機]]，在工廠裡使用[[齒輪|齒輪]]及揚水機，倡導[[水壩|水壩]]作為水力資源的源頭，為水磨及揚水機提供動力<ref name="Transmission"/>。這些建樹使中世紀伊斯蘭世界得以[[機械化|機械化]]，以[[機械|機械]]推動取代[[古代|古代]]的[[人力勞動|人力勞動]]。這些技術傳到中世紀的歐洲，對[[工業革命|工業革命]]產生了影響<ref name="Industrial"/>。

穆斯林農業革命催生了不少工業，包括早期的農業綜合企業、[[伊斯蘭天文學|天文儀器]]、[[陶瓷材料|陶瓷材料]]、[[化學工業|化學工業]]、[[蒸餾|蒸餾]]技術、[[時鐘|鐘錶]]、[[玻璃|玻璃]]、機械水電、風力機械、地蓆、[[鑲嵌畫|鑲嵌畫]]、紙漿和造紙、[[香水|香水]]、[[石油工業|石油工業]]、[[製藥業|製藥業]]、製繩、航運、造船、[[絲綢|絲綢]]、製糖、[[紡織業|紡織業]]、[[水利產業|水利產業]]、軍工、採礦（如硫、氨、鉛、鐵）。早期的大型工業區都是為這些工業而建，這些產業的知識技術後來傳到歐洲，特別是在12世紀[[拉丁文翻譯運動|拉丁文翻譯運動]]前後。11世紀，埃及工匠在希臘建成了第一所歐洲的玻璃工廠<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=.history-science-technology.com |title=Transfer Of Islamic Technology To The West, Part 1: Avenues Of Technology Transfer |url=http://www.history-science-technology.com/Articles/articles%207.htm |author=Ahmad Y Hassan |accessdate=4-11-2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080226105646/http://www.history-science-technology.com/Articles/articles%207.htm |archivedate=2008-02-26 }}</ref>。農業和手工業都在這個時期經歷了高速的發展<ref name="Capitalism"/>。

=== 勞工 ===
阿拉伯帝國的勞工具有不同的種族及宗教背景，男女也投身於不同的職業及經濟活動<ref>''Labour in the medieval Islamic world''，第6-7頁</ref>。婦女被廣泛僱用在各種商業活動上<ref name="Labour400">''Labour in the medieval Islamic world''，第400-401頁</ref>，包括第一產業（如農夫）、第二產業（[[建築工人|建築工人]]、[[染料|染料]]工人、紡紗工人等）及第三產業（[[投資者|投資者]]、[[醫生|醫生]]、[[護理人員|護理人員]]、[[工會|工會]]領袖、[[經紀人|經紀人]]、[[小販|小販]]、[[貸款|放款人]]、學者等）<ref>''Labour in the medieval Islamic world''，第350-362頁</ref>。穆斯林女性壟斷了紡織工業的某些工作範疇<ref name="Labour400"/>。

[[阿拉伯奴隸貿易|阿拉伯奴隸貿易]]活躍，交易會在伊斯蘭的邊境進行，接著奴隸就會被帶到人口聚集的地區，那裡的[[奴隷制度|奴隸市場]]會把奴隸分銷<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = BBC News | title = Focus on the slave trade | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1523100.stm | date = 03-09-2001 | accessdate = 5-11-2009 | archive-date = 2011-07-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110728134034/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1523100.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = JewishEncyclopedia.com | title = slave-trade | url = http://www.jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=849&letter=S | author = Isidore Singer、Joseph Jacobs | accessdate = 5-11-2009 | archive-date = 2010-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100215055140/http://jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=849&letter=S | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = britannica.com | title = Slavery | url = http://www.britannica.com/blackhistory/article-24159 | accessdate = 5-11-2009 | archive-date = 2014-10-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141014220905/http://www.britannica.com/blackhistory/article-24159 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。奴隸在伊斯蘭世界的經濟活動上佔著重要的地位<ref>{{cite web | language = en | title = Islam and Slavery | url = http://www.lse.ac.uk/collections/economicHistory/GEHN/GEHNPDF/Islam&SlaveryWGCS.pdf | author = William Gervase Clarence-Smith | accessdate = 5-11-2009 | archive-date = 2009-07-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090708150750/http://www.lse.ac.uk/collections/economicHistory/GEHN/GEHNPDF/Islam%26SlaveryWGCS.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = voi.org | title = Muslim Slave System in Medieval India | url = http://voi.org/books/mssmi/ | author = K.S. Lal | accessdate = 5-11-2009 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080512073030/http://voi.org/books/mssmi/ | archive-date = 2008-05-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。大量的奴隸自東非入口，他們主要在[[鹽礦|鹽礦]]及勞動密集的種植園工作。九世紀時[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]奴隸牽涉在內的[[津芝叛乱|津芝叛乱]]就是最佳的證明<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Michael Moïssey Postan、Edward Miller、Cynthia Postan | title = ''The Cambridge Economic History of Europe: Trade and industry in the Middle Ages'' | date = 1987年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 0-521-08709-0 | pages = 第417頁 }}</ref>。此外，奴隸還被用於家務工作<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=Salon.com |title=Islam's black slaves |url=http://archive.salon.com/books/int/2001/04/05/segal/index.html |author=Suzy Hansen |date=05-04-2001 |accessdate=5-11-2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070301113533/http://archive.salon.com/books/int/2001/04/05/segal/index.html |archivedate=2007-03-01 }}</ref>、兵役<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=Brooklyn College |title=The Mutual Effects of the Islamic and Judeo-Christian Worlds: The East European Pattern |url=http://coursesa.matrix.msu.edu/~fisher/hst373/readings/inalcik6.html |author=A. Ascher、B. K. Kiraly、T. Halasi-Kun |date=1979年 |accessdate=5-11-2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090911101051/http://coursesa.matrix.msu.edu/~fisher/hst373/readings/inalcik6.html |archivedate=2009-09-11 }}</ref>及民政<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = BBC | title = Economic slavery in Islam | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/religion/religions/islam/history/slavery_5.shtml | accessdate = 5-11-2009 | archive-date = 2009-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090816041417/http://www.bbc.co.uk/religion/religions/islam/history/slavery_5.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。中歐和東歐的奴隸被稱為[[薩卡里巴|薩卡里巴]]，來自中亞及高加索的奴隸被稱為[[馬木留克|馬木留克]]<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Oxford Univ Press | title = Bernard Lewis. Race and Slavery in the Middle East | url = http://www.fordham.edu/halsall/med/lewis1.html | date = 1994年 | accessdate = 5-11-2009 | archive-date = 2014-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140916112451/http://www.fordham.edu/halsall/med/lewis1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 技術 ===
{{main|伊斯蘭世界的發明}}
[[File:Al-jazari_robots.jpg|thumb]]

中世紀的穆斯林技師及發明家如{{link-en|阿拔斯·伊本·弗納斯|Abbas Ibn Firnas}}、{{link-en|巴努·穆薩|Banū Mūsā}}、[[賈札里|賈札里]]等發明了大量的新發明。

相信是出自伊斯蘭黃金時代的發明包括[[暗箱|暗箱]]、[[咖啡|咖啡]]、[[肥皂|肥皂]]、[[潔齒劑|潔齒劑]]、[[洗髮精|洗髮精]]、蒸餾、[[液化|液化]]、[[結晶|結晶]]、[[提純|提純]]、[[氧化|氧化]]、[[蒸發|蒸發]]、[[過濾|過濾]]、蒸餾酒、[[尿酸|尿酸]]、[[硝酸|硝酸]]、[[蒸餾器|蒸餾器]]、[[活門|活門]]、往復式吸入活塞泵、機動[[水鐘|水鐘]]、[[刺繡|刺繡]]、[[手術刀|手術刀]]、[[骨鋸|骨鋸]]、[[鑷子|鑷子]]、[[外科腸線|外科腸線]]、垂直軸[[風車|風車]]、[[接芽|接芽]]、[[種痘|種痘]]、[[鋼筆|鋼筆]]、[[密碼分析|密碼分析]]、[[頻率分析|頻率分析]]、三餐、[[花窗玻璃|花窗玻璃]]、[[熔凝石英|熔凝石英]]、[[波斯地毯|波斯地毯]]及[[渾象|渾象]]<ref name="Inventors">{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The Independent | title = How Islamic Inventors Changed the World | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/how-islamic-inventors-changed-the-world-469452.html | author = Paul Vallely | date = 11-03-2006 | accessdate = 05-11-2009 | archive-date = 2012-07-16 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20120716070311/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/how-islamic-inventors-changed-the-world-469452.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 城市化 ===
隨著[[城市化|城市化]]的發展，許多穆斯林的城市不經調節地擴張，形成以不同種族和宗教背景而劃分出來的狹窄而彎曲的街道及城區<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Khalid M. Al-Ankary、el-Sayed Bushra | title = ''Urban and rural profiles in Saudi Arabia'' | date = 1989年 | publisher = G. Borntraeger | isbn = 3-443-37010-1 | pages = 第128頁 }}</ref>。圍城之外則是市郊，由富裕的社區及半貧民窟組成。垃圾場及墓地則遠離市區，用作祈禱的地區可在主城門的附近找到，宗教節日的活動及公開處決也在那裡進行。軍營也在主城門附近。

穆斯林城市擁有先進的[[自來水|自來水]]系統，配備[[下水道|下水道]]、[[公共浴場|公共浴場]]、[[飲水機|飲水機]]、供應飲用水的管道<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Fiona MacDonald | title = ''The Plague and Medicine in the Middle Ages'' | date = 2006年 | publisher = Gareth Stevens | isbn = 0-8368-5907-3 | pages = 第42-43頁 }}</ref>、普及的私人和[[公共廁所|公共廁所]]及[[沐浴|沐浴]]設施<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Tor Eigeland | title = The Tiles of Iberia | journal = Saudi Aramco World | pages = 24-31 | year = 1992 }}</ref>。

因農業革命及醫療的改善，伊斯蘭土地上的平均[[預期壽命|預期壽命]]都得到提升。與古[[希臘－羅馬世界|希臘－羅馬世界]]對比（22至28歲）<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Encyclopædia Britannica Online | title = Life expectancy | url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/340119/life-expectancy | date = 2009 | accessdate = 06-11-2009 | archive-date = 2015-03-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150313014152/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/340119/life-expectancy | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = University of Wyoming | title = Americans and their health - A little good news | url = http://www.uwyo.edu/WINWyoming/bullets/2004/bullets11-04.htm | author = Betty Holmes | accessdate = 06-11-2009 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060828065116/http://www.uwyo.edu/winwyoming/bullets/2004/bullets11-04.htm | archive-date = 2006-08-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，早期伊斯蘭阿拉伯帝國的平均預期壽命高出了超過35年<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Lawrence I. Conrad | title = ''The Western Medical Tradition'' | date = 2006年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 0-521-47564-3 | pages = 第137頁 }}</ref>。[[阿訇|阿訇]]的平均預期壽命特別高，阿訇在十至十一世紀伊拉克和波斯的平均壽命達到84.3歲<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Richard W. Bulliet | title = ''The Age Structure of Medieval Islamic Education'' | journal = Studia Islamica | volume = 57 | pages = 105-117 | year = 1983 | doi = 10.2307/1595484 }}</ref>、在11世紀的中東達到72.8歲、11世紀的[[安達盧斯|安達盧斯]]達到69至75歲<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Maya Shatzmiller | title = ''Labour in the Medieval Islamic World''  | date = 1994年 | publisher = Brill Publishers | isbn = 90-04-09896-8 | pages = 第66頁 }}</ref>、十二世紀的波斯達到75歲<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Richard W. Bulliet | title = ''A Quantitative Approach to Medieval Muslim Biographical Dictionaries'' | journal = Journal of the Economic and Social History of the Orient | volume = 13 | issue = 2 | pages = 195-211 | year = 1970 }}</ref>、13世紀的波斯達到59至72歲<ref name="Authority">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Ahmad Atif Ahmad | title = ''Authority, Conflict, and the Transmission of Diversity in Medieval Islamic Law by R. Kevin Jaques'' | journal = Journal of Islamic Studies | volume = 18 | issue = 2 | pages = 246-248 | year = 2007 }}</ref>。伊斯蘭帝國的[[識字率|識字率]]亦得到增長，識字率是中世紀時期最高的，可與古典時期的希臘媲美，覆蓋的範圍比之更大<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Hoover Institution | title = Delivering Education | url = http://media.hoover.org/documents/0817928928_105.pdf | author = Andrew J. Coulson | accessdate = 06-11-2009 | archive-date = 2011-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110817054244/http://media.hoover.org/sites/default/files/documents/0817928928_105.pdf }}</ref>。

== 科學 ==
{{see|中世紀伊斯蘭世界的科學}}
對伊斯蘭科學的傳統觀點認為，它是古代知識的保存及傳達者<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Bertrand Russell | title = History of Western Philosophy | url = https://archive.org/details/historyofwestern00russ | date = 1945 | chapter = X}}</ref>，唐納德·拉赫主張源自歐洲的現代科學是中世紀科技及希臘學術的綜合體<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Donald F. Lach | title = ''Asia in the Making of Europe. A Century of Wonder, Vol. 2, Book 3'' | date = 1977年 | publisher = University of Chicago Press | isbn = 0-226-46734-1 | pages = 第397頁 }}</ref>。這類觀點在現代引起了爭論。一些學者認為穆斯林科學家為現代科學奠下基礎<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Robert Briffault | title = ''The Making of Humanity'' | url = https://archive.org/details/cu31924029765819 | date = 1928年 | publisher = G. Allen & Unwin Ltd | pages = 第191頁 }}</ref><ref name="Faith">{{cite book | language = en | author = Will Durant | title = ''The Age of Faith (The Story of Civilization, Volume 4)'' | date = 1980年 | publisher = Simon & Schuster | isbn = 0-671-01200-2 | pages = 第162-186頁 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Fielding H. Garrison | title = ''An introduction to the history of medicine: with medical chronology, suggestions for study and bibliographic data'' | url = https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.63857 | date = 1924年 | publisher = W.B. Saunders Company | pages = 第86頁 }}</ref><ref name="Miracle">{{cite book | language = en | author = Dr. Kasem Ajram | title = ''Miracle of Islamic Science'' | date =  | publisher = Knowledge House Publishers | isbn = 0-911119-43-4 | pages = Appendix B }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Muhammad Iqbal | title = ''The Reconstruction of Religious Thought in Islam'' | date = 1999年 | publisher = Kazi Publications | isbn = 0-686-18482-3 }}</ref>，發展出早期的[[科學方法|科學方法]]及對科學探究的[[經驗主義|經驗]]、[[實驗|實驗]]及[[定量|定量]]方法<ref name="Al-Haytham">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Rosanna Gorini | title = ''Al-Haytham the man of experience. First steps in the science of vision'' | url = http://www.ishim.net/ishimj/4/10.pdf | journal = Journal of the International Society for the History of Islamic Medicine | volume = 2 | issue = 4 | pages = 53-55 | year = 2003 | access-date = 2009-11-06 | archive-date = 2019-07-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190717022851/http://www.ishim.net/ishimj/4/10.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。有些學者將這段時期稱為「穆斯林[[科學革命|科學革命]]」<ref name="Astronomy"/><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Abdus Salam、H. R. Dalafi、Mohamed Hassan | title = ''Renaissance of Sciences in Islamic Countries'' | date = 1994年 | publisher = World Scientific | isbn = 9971-5-0713-7 | pages = 第162頁 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Abid Ullah Jan | title = ''After fascism: Muslims and the struggle for self-determination'' | chapter = Islam, the West, and the Question of Dominance | date = 2006年 | publisher = Pragmatic Publishings | isbn = 978-0-9733687-5-8 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = FSTC | title = An Introduction to Muslim Science | url = http://www.muslimheritage.com/uploads/Introduction_to_Muslim%20Science.pdf | date = 2003年 | accessdate = 07-11-2009 | archive-date = 2020-12-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201205185051/https://muslimheritage.com/uploads/Introduction_to_Muslim%20Science.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，用以表達穆斯林所取得的科學成就是由伊斯蘭教所推動<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Ahmad Y Hassan、Donald Routledge Hill  | title = ''Islamic Technology: An Illustrated History'' | date = 1986年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | pages = 第282頁 }}</ref>，不應與[[近代史|近代]]歐洲的科學革命混為一談<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Thomas Kuhn | title = The Copernican Revolution | url = https://archive.org/details/copernicanrevolu0000kuhn_l7c7 | date = 1957年 | publisher = Harvard Univ. Pr. | pages = 第142頁 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = H. Butterfield | title = ''The Origins of modern science 1300-1800'' | date = 1962年 | publisher = Collier Books }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = R. Hooykaas | title = The Rise of Modern Science: When and Why | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-for-the-history-of-science_1987-12_20_65/page/453 | journal = The British Journal for the History of Science | volume = 20 | pages = 453-473 | year = 1987 }}</ref>。[[愛德華·格蘭特|愛德華·格蘭特]]（Edward Grant）認為現代科學是希臘、伊斯蘭及拉丁文明匯聚而成<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Edward Grant | title = ''The foundations of modern science in the Middle Ages: their religious, institutional, and intellectual contexts'' | date = 1996年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 0-521-56762-9 }}</ref>。

=== 科學方法 ===
早期的科學方法源自伊斯蘭世界，締造了科學方法的重大進展，特別是11世紀[[海什木|海什木]]的成果，他被視為[[實驗物理學|實驗物理學]]的開創者<ref name="Al-Haytham"/><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Georgiĭ Vladimirovich Rozenberg  | title = Twilight: a study in atmospheric optics | url = https://archive.org/details/twilightstudyina0000roze | date = 1966年 | publisher = Plenum Press | pages = 第2頁 }}</ref>。科學方法最重要的發展是[[實驗|實驗]]及[[量化_(數理邏輯)|量化]]的應用。海什木寫作了《[[光學書|光學書]]》（Book of Optics）一書，顯著地改善了[[光學|光學]]領域的發展，他以實驗證明[[光線|光線]]進入眼睛，所以產生影像，他發明了[[暗箱|暗箱]]去說明光線的物理性質<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = David C. Lindberg | title = ''The Theory of Pinhole Images from Antiquity to the Thirteenth Century'' | journal = Archive for History of the Exact Sciences | volume = 5 | pages = 154-176 | year = 1968 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = R. S. Elliott | title = ''Electromagnetics'' | url = https://archive.org/details/electromagnetics0000elli | date = 1966年 | chapter = 1 | publisher = McGraw-Hill }}</ref>。

海什木是首位採用科學方法的人，被視為「第一位科學家」<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Bradley Steffens | title = ''Ibn al-Haytham: First Scientist'' | url = https://archive.org/details/ibnalhaythamfirs00brad | date = 2007年 | publisher = Morgan Reynolds Pub | isbn = 1-5993-5024-6 }}</ref>，加上他對[[心理學|心理學]]及[[視知覺|視知覺]]方面取得的開拓性成果<ref>''Ibn al-Haytham: First Scientist''，第5章</ref><ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Reynor Mausfeld | title = ''From Number Mysticism to the MauBformel: Fechner's Pyschophysics in the Tradition of Mathesis Universalis'' | url = http://www.psychologie.uni-kiel.de/psychophysik/mausfeld/Fechner_engl.pdf | journal = International Society for Pyshophysics | pages = 19-23 | year = 2000 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090327110751/http://www.psychologie.uni-kiel.de/psychophysik/mausfeld/Fechner_engl.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-27 | access-date = 2009-11-07 }}</ref>，使他被視為[[精神物理學|精神物理學]]和[[實驗心理學|實驗心理學]]的先驅<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Omar Khaleefa | title = ''Who Is the Founder of Psychophysics and Experimental Psychology'' | journal = American Journal of Islamic Social Sciences | volume = 16 | issue = 2 | year = 1999 }}</ref>。

=== 同行評審 ===
[[醫學同行評審|醫學同行評審]]是指一個由醫生組成的委員會研究被呈上的醫療案例，以判定讓該案例是否符合醫療標準。最早的醫學同行評審可見於[[敍利亞|敍利亞]]的伊沙克·本·阿里·拉哈威所寫的《醫生的道德》。該著作與其他後期的阿拉伯醫學手冊都提到，訪醫在每次探望病人的時候都須要將病人的狀況記錄在一式兩份的筆記上。當病人康復或死亡後，該醫生的筆記會被當地由其他醫生組成的評議會檢閱，以此來決定該醫生的工作是否符合所要求的醫療標準。如果評審的結果是負面，執業醫生可能會面臨虐待病人的起訴<ref name="peer-review"/>。

由合資格的專家獨創的首個科學同行審查，是對研究發現的評估，科學同行審查在1731年由[[愛丁堡皇家學會|愛丁堡皇家學會]]出版的《醫學論說及評論》當中描述出來。現今的科學同行審查都是由此演變而來<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Dale J. Benos et al. | title = ''The Ups and Downs of Peer Review'' | journal = Advances in Physiology Education | volume = 31 | pages = 145-152 | year = 2007}}</ref>。

=== 天文學 ===
[[File:Ghotb2.jpg|thumb]]的手抄本，描述了周轉圓行星模型。]]

一些人將[[馬拉蓋|馬拉蓋]]（Maragha）學派及他們的先輩和後輩所取得的成就稱為「馬拉蓋革命」、「馬拉蓋學派革命」或「伊斯蘭復興前的科學革命」<ref name="Astronomy"/>。馬拉蓋學派對天文學的貢獻包括在[[哈里發|哈里發]][[阿布·阿拔斯·阿卜杜拉·馬蒙·本·哈倫|馬蒙]]時期在[[巴格達|巴格達]]建造了第一所[[天文台|天文台]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Peter J Nas | title = ''Urban Symbolism'' | date = 1993年 | publisher = Brill Academic Publishers | isbn = 90-04-09855-0 | pages = 第350頁 }}</ref>，又收集及更正了以往的數據，解決了[[地心說|地心說]]顯著的難題，發展出通用的[[星盤|星盤]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Robert E. Krebs | title = ''Groundbreaking Scientific Experiments, Inventions, and Discoveries of the Middle Ages and the Renaissance'' | date = 2004年 | publisher = Greenwood Press | isbn = 0-313-32433-6 | pages = 第196頁 }}</ref>，發明了大量天文用具。自天文學家[[巴努·穆薩|阿布·加法爾·穆罕默德·伊本·穆薩·伊本·沙基爾]]以後的[[天體物理學|天體物理學]]及[[天體力學|天體力學]]發現[[地球|地球]]的[[物理定律|物理定律]]同樣適用於[[天體|天體]]及[[天球|天球]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = George Saliba | title = ''Early Arabic Critique of Ptolemaic Cosmology: A Ninth-Century Text on the Motion of the Celestial Spheres'' | journal = Journal for the History of Astronomy | volume = 25 | pages = 115-141 | year = 1994 }}</ref>。[[比魯尼|比魯尼]]是第一位詳盡闡述天體現象實驗及從[[語義學|語義]]上區分天文學與[[占星學|占星學]]的學者<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = S. Pines | title = ''The Semantic Distinction between the Terms Astronomy and Astrology according to al-Biruni'' | journal = Isis | volume = 55 | issue = 3 | pages = 343-349 | year = 1964 }}</ref>。天文學家運用實驗觀察和實驗技術去觀測天文<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Toby Huff | title = ''The Rise of Early Modern Science'' | date = 2003年 | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 0-521-52994-8 | pages = 第326頁 }}</ref>。[[海什木|海什木]]發現天球並非[[固體|固體]]及高空的密度較低空為低<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Edward Rosen | title = ''The Dissolution of the Solid Celestial Spheres'' | journal = Journal of the History of Ideas | volume = 46 | issue = 1 | pages = 13-31 | year = 1985 }}</ref>，他和[[伊本·沙提爾|伊本·沙提爾]]（Ibn al-Shatir）將[[自然哲學|自然哲學]]從天文學拆分出來<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author =Roshdi Rashed | title = ''The Celestial Kinematics of Ibn al-Haytham'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_arabic-sciences-and-philosophy_2007-03_17_1/page/7 | journal = Arabic Sciences and Philosophy | volume = 17 | pages = 7-55 | year = 2007 }}</ref>。海什木又和[[穆艾葉德丁·烏爾迪|穆艾葉德丁·烏爾迪]]（Mo'ayyeduddin Urdi）構造了第一個非托密斯模型。伊本·沙提爾以實驗為依據，而不以[[哲學|哲學]]為依據來駁斥托密斯模型。[[納西爾丁·圖西|納西爾丁·圖西]]及[[阿里·古什吉|阿里·古什吉]]（Ali al-Qushji）首次以實驗觀察來證明[[地球自轉|地球自轉]]，還有[[比里安迪|比里安迪]]（Al-Birjandi）的早期「圓慣性」原理<ref name="Tusi">{{cite journal | language = en | author = F. Jamil Ragep | title = ''Tusi and Copernicus: The Earth's Motion in Context'' | journal = Science in Context | volume = 14 | issue = 1-2 | pages = 145-163 | year = 2001 }}</ref>。

多位穆斯林天文學家也推測地球沿其軸心自轉，並提出[[日心說|日心說]]的假說<ref name="Miracle"/><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Seyyed Hossein Nasr | title = ''An Introduction to Islamic Cosmological Doctrines'' | date = 1964年 | publisher = Belknap Press of the Harvard University Press | pages = 第135-136頁 }}</ref>。眾所周知，在以太陽為中心的背景下，[[尼古拉·哥白尼|尼古拉·哥白尼]]在《[[天體運行論|天體運行論]]》裡提出的[[哥白尼日心模型|哥白尼日心模型]]（Copernican heliocentric model）是取自[[伊本·沙提爾|伊本·沙提爾]]及馬拉蓋學派的[[地心說|地心說]]<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Columbia University | title = Whose Science is Arabic Science in Renaissance Europe? | url = http://www.columbia.edu/~gas1/project/visions/case1/sci.1.html | author = George Saliba | date = 1999年 | accessdate = 10-11-2009 | archive-date = 2008-01-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080115070924/http://www.columbia.edu/~gas1/project/visions/case1/sci.1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，哥白尼所主張的地球自轉與納西爾丁·圖西及阿里·古什吉的觀點近似<ref name="Tusi"/>。

=== 化學 ===
[[賈比爾|賈比爾]]被認為是化學的開拓者<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Zygmunt S. Derewenda | title = ''On wine, chirality and crystallography'' | journal = Acta Crystallographica Section A: Foundations of Crystallography | volume = 64 | pages = 246-258 | year = 2007 | doi = 10.1107/S0108767307054293 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = John Warren | title = ''War and the Cultural Heritage of Iraq: a sadly mismanaged affair'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_third-world-quarterly_2005_26_4-5/page/815 | journal = Third World Quarterly | volume = 26 | issue = 4-5 | pages = 815-830 | year = 2005}}</ref>，他引進了一些早期實驗性質的科學方法，還有[[蒸餾器|蒸餾器]]、[[製酒蒸餾器|製酒蒸餾器]]、[[曲頸瓶|曲頸瓶]]<ref name="Inventors"/>及純[[蒸餾|蒸餾]]、[[過濾|過濾]]、[[升華|升華]]<ref>''The Making of Humanity''，第195頁</ref>、[[液化|液化]]、[[結晶|結晶]]、[[提純|提純]]、[[氧化還原反應|氧化還原]]、[[蒸發|蒸發]]<ref name="Inventors"/>。

[[肯迪|肯迪]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Felix Klein-Frank | title = ''History of Islamic Philosophy'' | date = 2001年 | publisher = Routledge | pages = 第174頁 }}</ref>、[[比魯尼|比魯尼]]<ref>{{cite journal | language =en | author = Michael E. Marmura | title = ''An Introduction to Islamic Cosmological Doctrines. Conceptions of Nature and Methods Used for Its Study by the Ikhwan Al-Safa'an, Al-Biruni, and Ibn Sina by Seyyed Hossein Nasr'' | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_speculum_1965-10_40_4/page/744 | journal = Speculum  | volume = 40 | issue = 4 | pages = 744-746 | year = 1965 }}</ref>、[[伊本·西那|伊本·西那]]<ref>''The Making of Humanity''，第196-197頁</ref>及[[伊本·赫勒敦|伊本·赫勒敦]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = ʻAzīz ʻAẓmah | title = ''Arabic thought and Islamic societies'' | date = 1986年 | publisher = Routledge | isbn = 0-7099-0584-X | pages = 第203-204頁 }}</ref>先後批駁傳統[[煉金術|煉金術]]及[[賢者之石|賢者之石]]的論說。[[穆罕默德·伊本·扎卡里亞·拉齊|穆罕默德·伊本·扎卡里亞·拉齊]]在他的著作《蓋倫的疑惑》（Doubts about Galen）裡首次利用實驗來證明[[亞里士多德|亞里士多德]][[四元素說|四元素說]]及[[蓋倫|蓋倫]][[體液學說|體液學說]]（Humorism）的謬誤。[[納西爾丁·圖西|納西爾丁·圖西]]陳述了早期的[[質量守恆定律|質量守恆定律]]，認為[[物質|物質]]本身可以轉化，但是沒法消失<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Farid Alakbarov | title = ''A 13th-Century Darwin? Tusi's Views on Evolution'' | url = http://azer.com/aiweb/categories/magazine/92_folder/92_articles/92_tusi.html | journal = Azerbaijan International | volume = 9 | issue = 2 | year = 2001 | access-date = 2009-11-11 | archive-date = 2019-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190526010312/http://azer.com/aiweb/categories/magazine/92_folder/92_articles/92_tusi.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。學者[[亞歷山大·馮·洪堡|亞歷山大·馮·洪堡]]和[[威爾·杜蘭特|威爾·杜蘭特]]（Will Durant）認為中世紀的穆斯林化學家是化學的創立者<ref name="Faith"/><ref name="Miracle"/>。

=== 數學 ===
穆斯林數學家在這個時期的成就包括[[波斯人|波斯籍]]伊斯蘭數學家[[花剌子密|花剌子密]]發展的[[代數|代數]]及[[算法|算法]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Robert E. Krebs | title = ''Groundbreaking scientific experiments, inventions, and discoveries of the Middle Ages and the Renaissance'' | date = 2004年 | publisher = Greenwood Publishing Group | isbn = 0-313-32433-6 | pages = 第133頁 }}</ref>、[[球面三角學|球面三角學]]的發明<ref>''Islam and Science, Medicine, and Technology''，第18頁</ref>，在[[阿拉伯數字|阿拉伯數字]]裡加入應用[[小數點|小數點]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author =  | coauthors =  | title = ''Encyclopaedia of the history of science, technology, and medicine in non-western cultures'' | url = https://archive.org/details/encyclopaediaofh0000unse | date = 1997年 | publisher = Springer | isbn = 0-7923-4066-3 | pages = 第68頁 }}</ref>、除了正弦外所有[[三角函數|三角函數]]的發現<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Victor J. Katz、Annette Imhausen | title = ''The mathematics of Egypt, Mesopotamia, China, India, and Islam: a sourcebook'' | date = 2007年 | publisher = Princeton University Press | isbn = 0-691-11485-4 | pages = 第518頁 }}</ref>、[[肯迪|肯迪]]引入的[[密碼分析|密碼分析]]及頻率分析<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Karl de Leeuw、J. A. Bergstra | title = ''The history of information security: a comprehensive handbook'' | date = 2007年 | publisher = Elsevier | isbn = 0-444-51608-5 | pages = 第279頁 }}</ref>、[[卡拉吉|卡拉吉]]（Al-Karaji）引入的代數演算及運用[[數學歸納法|數學歸納法]][[證明|證明]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Neil Schlager、Josh Lauer | title = ''Science and Its Times: Understanding the Social Significance of Scientific Discovery'' | date = 2001年 | publisher = Gale Group | isbn = 0-7876-3934-6 | pages = 第237頁 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Arthur Knoebel、Reinhard Laubenbacher、Jerry Lodder、David Pengelley | title = ''Mathematical masterpieces: further chronicles by the explorers'' | date = 2007年 | publisher = Springer | isbn = 0-387-33061-5 | pages = 第7頁 }}</ref>、[[海什木|海什木]]的[[解析幾何|解析幾何]]及最早用於[[無窮小量|無窮小量]]及積分學的通用公式<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Josef W. Meri | title = ''Medieval Islamic Civilization: An Encyclopedia'' | date = 2005年 | publisher = Routledge | isbn = 0-415-96690-6 | pages = 第344頁 }}</ref>、[[歐瑪爾·海亞姆|歐瑪爾·海亞姆]]開創的[[代數幾何|代數幾何]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Rushdī Rāshid、Bijan Vahabzadeh | title = ''Omar Khayyam, the mathematician'' | date = 2000年 | publisher = Bibliotheca Persica Press | isbn = 0-933273-43-6 | pages = 第25頁 }}</ref>、[[納西爾丁·圖西|納西爾丁·圖西]]率先對[[歐幾里得幾何|歐幾里得幾何]]的反駁及其[[平行公設|平行公設]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Timothy Gowers、June Barrow-Green、Imre Leader | title = ''The Princeton companion to mathematics'' | date = 2008年 | publisher = Princeton University Press | pages = 第86-87頁 }}</ref>、薩德雷丁對[[非歐幾里得幾何|非歐幾里得幾何]]的率先涉獵<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Jeremy Gray  | title = ''Ideas of space: Euclidean, non-Euclidean, and relativistic'' | date = 1989年 | publisher = Oxford University Press | isbn = 0-19-853935-5 | pages = 第51頁 }}</ref>、[[阿布·哈桑·伊本·阿里·加拉薩迪|阿布·哈桑·伊本·阿里·加拉薩迪]]（Abū al-Hasan ibn Alī al-Qalasādī）的[[數學符號|數學符號]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Florian Cajori | title = ''A History of Mathematical Notations'' | url = https://archive.org/details/b29980343_0001 | date = 1929年 | publisher = The Open court publishing company | pages = 第86頁 }}</ref>以及其他大量在代數、[[算術|算術]]、微積分、[[密碼學|密碼學]]、[[幾何學|幾何學]]、[[數論|數論]]、[[三角學|三角學]]方面的發展。

=== 醫學 ===
[[File:Cheshm_manuscript.jpg|right]]

[[伊斯蘭醫學|伊斯蘭醫學]]受到各類不同的醫學體系影響，[[古希臘|古希臘]]及[[古羅馬|古羅馬]]醫學家[[希波克拉底|希波克拉底]]、[[迪奧斯科里斯|迪奧斯科里斯]]、[[以弗所的索拉努斯|索拉努斯]]、[[奧盧斯·科尼利厄斯·塞爾蘇斯|塞爾蘇斯]]及[[蓋倫|蓋倫]]的著作都對伊斯蘭醫學產生持久的影響<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = flinders.edu.au | title = Science, technology and medicine in the Roman Empire | url = http://www.es.flinders.edu.au/~mattom/science+society/lectures/lecture11.html | accessdate = 2009-11-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110429201149/http://www.es.flinders.edu.au/~mattom/science+society/lectures/lecture11.html | archive-date = 2011-04-29 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Oxford Journals | title = Tradition and Perspectives of Arab Herbal Medicine: A Review | url = http://ecam.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/2/4/475 | date = 2005-10-17 | accessdate = 2009-11-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100203062321/http://ecam.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/2/4/475 | archivedate = 2010-02-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = pacs.unica.it | title = Hellenistic-Roman Medicine. Arab Medicine. Medieval Times | url = http://pacs.unica.it/biblio/lesson2.htm | accessdate = 2009-11-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090919142155/http://pacs.unica.it/biblio/lesson2.htm | archive-date = 2009-09-19 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

穆斯林醫學家對[[醫學|醫學]]作出了許多重要的貢獻，包括[[解剖學|解剖學]]、[[醫學研究|醫學研究]]、[[眼科學|眼科學]]、[[病理學|病理學]]、[[製藥學|製藥學]]、[[生理學|生理學]]、[[外科學|外科學]]等。他們設立了一些最早的專科醫院<ref name="George Sarton">{{cite book | language = en | author = George Sarton | title = ''Introduction to the History of Science'' | url = https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.211923 | date = 1927年 | publisher = Published for the Carnegie Institution of Washington by the Williams & Wilkins Co.}}</ref>，包括第一所醫學院和第一所[[精神專科醫院|精神專科醫院]]<ref>{{cite web | language = en | title = ''A Short History of the Arab Peoples'' | url = http://www.cyberistan.org/islamic/quote2.html#glubb | author = Sir John Bagot Glubb | date = 1969年 | accessdate = 2009-11-13 | archive-date = 2019-05-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190523055629/http://www.cyberistan.org/islamic/quote2.html#glubb | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Hanafy A. Youssef、Fatma A. Youssef、T. R. Dening | title = ''Evidence for the existence of schizophrenia in medieval Islamic society'' | journal = History of Psychiatry | volume = 7 | pages = 55-62 | year = 1996 }}</ref>。[[肯迪|肯迪]]在他的著作《[[De_Gradibus|De Gradibus]]》裡說明了量化及數學在醫藥裡的應用，如以數學刻度來表示藥物的效用、計算病症最危急的時期<ref>''History of Islamic Philosophy''，第172頁</ref>。[[穆罕默德·伊本·扎卡里亞·拉齊|拉齊]]發現了[[麻疹|麻疹]]及[[天花|天花]]，又在他的《蓋倫的疑惑》裡論證了[[蓋倫|蓋倫]][[體液學說|體液學說]]的謬論。

醫學家[[宰赫拉威|宰赫拉威]]為現代[[外科學|外科學]]奠下了基礎<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = A. Martin-Araguz、C. Bustamante-Martinez、Ajo V. Fernandez-Armayor、J. M. Moreno-Martinez | title = ''Neuroscience in al-Andalus and its influence on medieval scholastic medicine'' | journal = Revista de neurología | volume = 34 | issue = 9 | pages = 877-892 | year = 2002}}</ref>，據他的《[[醫學寶鑒|醫學寶鑒]]》（al-Tasrif）裡記載，他發明了大量的[[外科手術|外科手術]]，包括分娩<ref name="Arab Herbal">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Bashar Saad、Hassan Azaizeh、Omar Said | title = ''Tradition and Perspectives of Arab Herbal Medicine: A Review'' | journal = Evidence-based Complementary and Alternative Medicine | volume = 2 | issue = 4 | pages = 475-479 | year = 2005}}</ref>、外科專用的[[腸線|腸線]]、[[手術鑷|手術鑷]]、[[結紮線|結紮線]]、[[外科縫合針|外科縫合針]]、[[手術刀|手術刀]]、[[刮匙|刮匙]]、[[牽開器|牽開器]]、手術匙、[[探子|探子]]、手術鈎、手術棒、[[窺鏡|窺鏡]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Khaled al-Hadidi  | title = ''The Role of Muslim Scholars in Oto-rhino-Laryngology'' | journal = The Egyptian Journal of O.R.L. | volume = 4 | issue = 1 | pages = 1-15 | year = 1978}}</ref>及骨鋸<ref name="Inventors"/>。[[海什木|海什木]]在《[[光學書|光學書]]》裡首先解釋了視覺和[[視知覺|視知覺]]的過程，推進了[[眼部手術|眼部手術]]的發展<ref name="Arab Herbal"/>。

[[伊本·西那|伊本·西那]]為現代醫學奠下了基礎<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Cas Lek Cesk | title = ''The father of medicine, Avicenna, in our science and culture: Abu Ali ibn Sina (980-1037)'' | journal = Becka J. | volume = 119 | issue = 1 | pages = 17-23 | year = 1980 }}</ref>，其著作《[[回回藥方|回回藥方]]》將系統化的實驗及量化應用到生理學裡<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Katharine Park | title = ''Avicenna in Renaissance Italy: The Canon and Medical Teaching in Italian Universities after 1500 by Nancy G. Siraisi'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-modern-history_1990-03_62_1/page/169 | journal = The Journal of Modern History | volume = 62 | issue = 1 | pages = 169-170 | year = 1990 }}</ref>，他發現了[[傳染病|傳染病]]及採用[[隔離檢疫|隔離檢疫]]措施來阻止傳染病擴散，引進[[醫學研究|醫學實驗]]、[[循證醫學|循證醫學]]、[[臨床試驗|臨床試驗]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = David W. Tschanz | title = ''Arab Roots of European Medicine'' | journal = Heart Views | volume = 4 | issue = 2 | year = 2003 }}</ref>、[[隨機對照試驗|隨機對照試驗]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Jonathan D. Eldredge | title = ''The Randomised Controlled Trial design: unrecognized opportunities for health sciences librarianship'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_health-information-and-libraries-journal_2003-03_20_1/page/34 | journal = Health Information and Libraries Journal | volume = 20 | pages = 34-44 | year = 2003 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author =  | title = ''Evaluation Of Randomized Controlled Trials On Complementary And Alternative Medicine'' | journal = International Journal of Technology Assessment in Health Care | volume = 16 | issue = 1 | pages = 13-21 | year = 2000 }}</ref>、效能測試<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = D. Craig Brater、Walter J. Daly | title = ''Clinical pharmacology in the Middle Ages: Principles that presage the 21st century'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_clinical-pharmacology-and-therapeutics_2000-04_67_5/page/447 | journal = Clinical Pharmacology & Therapeutics | volume = 67 | issue = 5 | pages = 447-450 | year = 2000 }}</ref><ref name="clinical medicine">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Walter J. Daly、D. Craig Brater | title = ''Medieval contributions to the search for truth in clinical medicine'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_perspectives-in-biology-and-medicine_summer-2000_43_4/page/530 | journal = Perspectives in Biology and Medicine | volume = 43 | issue = 4 | pages = 530-540 | year = 2000 }}</ref>及[[臨床藥理學|臨床藥理學]]<ref name="clinical medicine"/>，又首先描述了[[細菌|細菌]]和病毒<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The American Institute of Unani Medicine | title = The Canon of Medicine | url = http://www.unani.com/avicenna%20story%203.htm | date = 2003 | accessdate = 2009-11-16 | archive-date = 2009-08-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090806073311/http://www.unani.com/avicenna%20story%203.htm | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，區分出[[胸膜炎|胸膜炎]]與[[縱膈炎|縱膈炎]]。除此之外，他又發現了[[結核|結核]]的傳染性、[[疾病|疾病]]透過水、土壤、表皮接觸、[[性傳播疾病|性]]、[[反常行為|反常行為]]、神經系統傳播<ref name="George Sarton"/>，利用冰來治理[[發熱|發熱]]徵狀及區分醫學及藥理學<ref name="Arab Herbal"/>。

[[伊本·蘇爾|伊本·蘇爾]]是已知最早的實驗外科醫生<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Rabie E. Abdel-Halim | title = ''Contributions of Muhadhdhab Al-Deen Al-Baghdadi to the progress of medicine and urology'' | journal = Saudi Medical Journal | volume = 27 | issue = 11 | pages = 1631-1641 | year = 2006 }}</ref>，他在12世紀將試驗法引入到外科手術，他是在對病人實施外科手術之前進行[[動物試驗|動物試驗]]的第一人<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author =  | title = ''Contributions of Ibn Zuhr (Avenzoar) to the progress of surgery: A study and translations from his book Al-Taisir'' | journal = Saudi Medical Journal 2005 | volume = 26 | issue = 9 | pages = 1333-1339 | year = 2005}}</ref>，又首先對人類和動物實施[[解剖|解剖]]及[[驗屍|驗屍]]<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Hutchinson Encyclopedia | title = Islamic medicine | url = http://encyclopedia.farlex.com/Islamic+medicine | accessdate = 2009-11-16 | archive-date = 2012-02-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208031923/http://encyclopedia.farlex.com/Islamic+medicine | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

[[伊本·納菲斯|伊本·納菲斯]]則為[[心血管生理學|心血管生理學]]奠下基礎<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Chairman's Reflections | title = ''Traditional Medicine Among Gulf Arabs, Part II: Blood-letting'' | journal = Heart Views | volume = 5 | issue = 2 | pages = 74-85 | year = 2004 }}</ref>，他是描述[[肺循環|肺循環]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = S. A. Al-Dabbagh | title = ''Ibn Al-Nafis and the pulmonary circulation'' | journal = The Lancet | volume = 1 | pages = 1148 | year = 1978 }}</ref>和[[冠狀血管|冠狀血管]]的第一人<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author =  | title = ''Ibn al-Nafīs: A Biographical Sketch of the Discoverer of Pulmonary and Coronary Circulation'' | journal = Journal of the International Society for the History of Islamic Medicine | volume = 1 | pages = 22-28 | year = 2003 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Matthijs Oudkerk | title = ''Coronary Radiology'' | url = https://archive.org/details/coronaryradiolog0000unse_2ed | date = 2004年 | publisher = Springer Science+Business Media | isbn = 3-540-43640-5 | chapter = Preface }}</ref>，構建了[[循環系統|循環系統]]的基礎，因而被視為中世紀「最偉大的生理學家」<ref>{{cite web |language=en |publisher=Encyclopedia of Islamic World |title=The West denies Ibn Al Nafis's contribution to the discovery of the circulation |url=http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/drpaul.html |accessdate=2009-11-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090825102842/http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/drpaul.html |archivedate=2009-08-25 }}</ref>。他又是[[代謝|代謝]]概念的第一個描述者<ref name="Ibn al-Nafis">{{cite web |language=en |publisher=Encyclopedia of Islamic World |title=Ibn al-Nafis As a Philosopher |url=http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/drroubi.html |accessdate=2009-11-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080206072116/http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/drroubi.html |archivedate=2008-02-06 }}</ref>，不相信[[伊本·西那|伊本·西那]]及[[蓋倫|蓋倫]]的[[體液學說|體液學說]]、[[脈搏|脈搏]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Nahyan A. G. Fancy | title = ''Pulmonary Transit and Bodily Resurrection: The Interaction of Medicine, Philosophy and Religion in the Works of Ibn al-Nafīs (d. 1288)'' | journal = Electronic Theses and Dissertations | url = http://etd.nd.edu/ETD-db/theses/available/etd-11292006-152615/ | pages = 3、6 | year = 2006 | access-date = 2009-11-16 | archive-date = 2015-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150404020329/http://etd.nd.edu/ETD-db/theses/available/etd-11292006-152615/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>、[[骨骼|骨骼]]、[[肌肉|肌肉]]、[[腸臟|腸臟]]、[[感覺器|感覺器]]、[[膽汁管|膽汁管]]、[[食道|食道]]、[[胃|胃]]等理論，並創立了[[生理學|生理學]]及[[心理學|心理學]]的新模式來取代它們<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Encyclopedia of Islamic World | title = ''Ibn ul Nafis has dissected the human body'' | author = Dr. Sulaiman Oataya | url = http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/index.html | accessdate = 2009-11-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091023065405/http://www.islamset.com/isc/nafis/index.html | archivedate = 2009-10-23 }}</ref>。

伊本·盧布迪不認同體液學說，他發現對身體的保存取決於[[血液|血液]]、女性不能生產[[精子|精子]]、動脈的活動不依賴於[[心臟|心臟]]的活動、心臟是胎兒形成的第一個器官、[[顱骨|顱骨]]可生成[[腫瘤|腫瘤]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = L. Leclerc | title = ''Histoire de la medecine Arabe'' | date = 1876年  | volume = 2 | pages = 第161頁 }}</ref>。伊本·克蒂馬及伊本·哈提卜發現[[微生物|微生物]]入體可致傳染病<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Ibrahim B. Syed | title = ''Islamic Medicine: 1000 years ahead of its times'' | journal = Journal of the Islamic Medical Association | volume = 2 | pages = 2-9 | year = 2002 }}</ref>。[[曼蘇爾·伊本·伊利亞斯|曼蘇爾·伊本·伊利亞斯]]（Mansur ibn Ilyas）繪畫了人體結構、[[神經系統|神經系統]]及[[循環系統|循環系統]]的詳細圖像<ref name="Science"/>。

=== 物理學 ===
[[海什木|海什木]]開創了對[[實驗物理學|實驗物理學]]的研究<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Rüdiger Thiele | title = ''In Memoriam: Matthias Schramm'' | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_arabic-sciences-and-philosophy_2005-09_15_2/page/329 | journal = Arabic Sciences and Philosophy | volume = 15 | pages = 329-331 | year = 2005 }}</ref>，他是現代[[光學|光學]]的開拓者，其著作《[[光學書|光學書]]》倡議實驗科學方法，以此徹底轉變人們對[[光|光]]及[[視知覺|視知覺]]的認識。《光學書》開創了光學及視知覺的[[科學革命|科學革命]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = A. I. Sabra、J. P. Hogendijk | title = ''The Enterprise of Science in Islam: New Perspectives'' | date = 2003年 | publisher = MIT Press | isbn = 0-262-19482-1 | pages = 第85-118頁 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = F. J. Ragep、Sally P. Ragep、Steven John Livesey | title = ''Tradition, Transmission, Transformation: Proceedings of Two Conferences on Pre-modern Science held at the University of Oklahoma'' | url = https://archive.org/details/loptiquedeclaude0000ptol | date = 1996年 | publisher = Brill Publishers | isbn = 90-04-09126-2 | pages = 第500頁 }}</ref>，因而被[[艾薩克·牛頓|艾薩克·牛頓]]的《[[自然哲學的數學原理|自然哲學的數學原理]]》評為[[物理學史|物理學史]]上最具影響力的書籍之一<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = H. Salih、M. Al-Amri、M. El Gomati | title = ''The Miracle of Light'' | journal = A World of Science | volume = 3 | issue = 3 | year = 2005 }}</ref>。

[[比魯尼|比魯尼]]則將實驗科學方法應用到[[力學|力學]]上<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Mariam Rozhanskaya、I. S. Levinova  | title = ''Encyclopedia of the History of Arabic Science'' | date = 1996年 | publisher = Routledge | volume = 2 | pages = 第614-624頁 }}</ref>，多位穆斯林科學則發現了[[牛頓運動定律|牛頓運動定律]]的前身。牛頓的第一個運動定律[[慣性定理|慣性定理]]及[[動量|動量]]是由[[海什木|海什木]]和[[伊本·西那|伊本·西那]]所發現<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Abdus Salam | title = ''Ideals and Realities: Selected Essays of Abdus Salam'' | date = 1987年 | publisher = World Scientific | pages = 第179-213頁 }}</ref><ref name="Fernando">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Fernando Espinoza | title = ''An analysis of the historical development of ideas about motion and its implications for teaching'' | journal = Physics Education | volume = 40 | issue = 2 | pages = 第141頁 | year = 2005 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Seyyed Hossein Nasr | title = ''Dictionary of the History of Ideas'' | date = 1973年 | location = New York | publisher = Charles Scribner's Sons | pages = 第65頁 }}</ref>。[[力|力]]和[[加速度|加速度]]的比值是由[[希巴特·阿拉·艾布柏巴拉卡特·巴格達迪|希巴特·阿拉·艾布柏巴拉卡特·巴格達迪]]（Hibat Allah Abu'l-Barakat al-Baghdaadi）所發現，這是「[[經典力學|經典力學]]的基本法則」，為牛頓的第二個運動定律埋下伏筆<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Shlomo Pines | title = ''Dictionary of Scientific Biography'' | date = 1970年 | publisher = Charles Scribner's Sons | isbn = 0-684-10114-9 | pages = 第26-28頁 }}</ref>。後來演變成牛頓第三個運動定律的[[反作用力|反作用力]]則由[[伊本·巴哲|伊本·巴哲]]所發現<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Shlomo Pines | title = ''Avempace, Projectile Motion, and Impetus Theory'' | journal = Journal of the History of Ideas | volume = 64 | issue = 4 | pages = 521-546 | year = 1964 }}</ref>。[[巴努·穆薩兄弟|加爾法·穆罕默德·伊本·穆薩·伊本·沙基爾]]（Ja'far Muhammad ibn Mūsā ibn Shākir）<ref>''The Making of Humanity''，第191頁</ref>、[[海什木|海什木]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Nader El-Bizri | volume = 2 | title = ''Medieval Islamic Civilization: An Encyclopaedia'' | date = 2006年 | publisher = Routledge | pages = 第343-345頁 }}</ref>及[[哈齊尼|哈齊尼]]（Al-Khazini）為[[牛頓萬有引力定律|牛頓萬有引力定律]]鋪墊了一些相關的理論<ref>''Encyclopaedia of the History of Arabic Science''，第2冊，第622頁</ref>。伊本·西那對[[伽利略·伽利萊|伽利略·伽利萊]]的[[加速度|加速度]]數理及他的慣性原理受進行評註而使之更加充實<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Galileo Galilei | title = ''Two New Sciences'' | url = https://archive.org/details/twonewsciencesin0000gali | date = 1974年 | publisher = Univ. of Wisconsin Pr. | pages =  第217、225、296-297頁}}</ref><ref name="Fernando"/>。

=== 其他科學 ===
穆斯林科學家也壟促進了[[生物學|生物學]]（[[解剖學|解剖學]]、[[植物學|植物學]]、[[演化|演化]]、[[生理學|生理學]]、[[動物學|動物學]]）、[[地球科學|地球科學]]（[[人類學|人類學]]、[[地圖學|地圖學]]、[[大地測量學|大地測量學]]、[[地理學|地理學]]、[[地質學|地質學]]）、[[心理學|心理學]]（[[實驗心理學|實驗心理學]]、[[精神病學|精神病學]]、[[精神物理學|精神物理學]]及[[心理治療|心理治療]]）及[[社會科學|社會科學]]（[[人口學|人口學]]、[[經濟學|經濟學]]、[[社會學|社會學]]、[[歷史|歷史]]、[[歷史學|歷史學]]）方面的進步。

伊斯蘭黃金時代其他的一些知名科學家包括[[法拉比|法拉比]]、[[比魯尼|比魯尼]]（最早的[[人類學|人類學]]家及[[大地測量學|大地測量學]]的開創者）<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Akbar S. Ahmed | title = ''Al-Beruni: The First Anthropologist'' | date = 1984年 | pages = 第9-10頁 }}</ref>、[[納西爾丁·圖西|納西爾丁·圖西]]、[[伊本·赫勒敦|伊本·赫勒敦]]（被視為[[社會科學|社會科學]]一些範疇的開創者<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Akbar Ahmed | title = ''Ibn Khaldun’s Understanding of Civilizations and the Dilemmas of Islam and the West Today'' | journal = Middle East Journal | volume = 56 | issue = 1 | pages =  | year = 2002}}</ref>，如[[人口學|人口學]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = H. Mowlana | title = ''Information in the Arab World'' | journal = Cooperation South Journal | volume = 1 | year = 2001}}</ref>、[[經濟學|經濟學]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = I. M. Oweiss | title = ''Arab Civilization: Challenges and Responses'' | date = 1988年 | publisher = New York University Press | isbn = 0-88706-698-4 | pages = 第112-128頁 }}</ref>、[[文化史|文化史]]<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Mohamad Abdalla | title = ''Ibn Khaldun on the Fate of Islamic Science after the 11th Century'' | journal = Islam & Science | volume = 5 | issue = 1 | pages = 61-70 | year = 2007 }}</ref>、[[歷史學|歷史學]]<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Salahuddin Ahmed | title = ''A Dictionary of Muslim Names'' | date = 1999年 | publisher = C. Hurst & Co. Publishers | isbn = 1-85065-356-9 }}</ref>及[[社會學|社會學]]<ref name="Akhtar">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Dr. S. W. Akhtar | title = ''The Islamic Concept of Knowledge'' | journal = Al-Tawhid: A Quarterly Journal of Islamic Thought & Culture | volume = 12 | issue = 3 | year = 1997}}</ref>）。

== 其他成就 ==
=== 建築 ===
{{main|伊斯蘭建築}}
[[File:TajMahalbyAmalMongia.jpg|thumb]][[阿格拉|阿格拉]]的[[泰姬陵|泰姬陵]]，建於[[莫臥兒帝國|莫臥兒帝國]]時期。]]
